Design Intent (Built for Work)
I'm:
Welding
Doing mechanical service
Working poultry houses
Farm repair / fence / cattle
Automotive diagnostics
So this bed needs:
✔ Tool storage
✔ Generator mount
✔ Welder mount
✔ Tie-down points
✔ Rear receiver
✔ Strong but not overweight
✔ Easy to fabricate in the shop

Run lengthwise:
(2) 3" x 2" x 0.188 wall rectangular tubing
Length: 67"
These sit directly over truck frame rails
These carry 80% of the load.